    <div class="sg">
      <div class="sc"><div class="sn">1</div><h4>Link &amp; Tag</h4><p>Link the Business Profile to Google Ads and install the Google tag (via Google Tag Manager) on the Wix site.</p></div>
      <div class="sc"><div class="sn">2</div><h4>Primary conversions</h4><p>Store visits (from Location Asset), phone calls (60-sec min), and "Get Directions" clicks.</p></div>
      <div class="sc"><div class="sn">3</div><h4>Secondary signals</h4><p>Key page views — product pages, "What's In Stock," and Contact/Hours page — plus time-on-site.</p></div>
      <div class="sc"><div class="sn">4</div><h4>Baseline</h4><p>Record Business Profile Insights (views, calls, direction requests) before launch to measure lift.</p></div>
      <div class="sc"><div class="sn">5</div><h4>Set priority</h4><p>Mark store visits &amp; calls as primary; page views as secondary so bidding optimizes toward real intent.</p></div>
      <div class="sc"><div class="sn">6</div><h4>Reconcile</h4><p>Cross-check ad-driven leads with actual in-store / phone sales monthly to confirm true ROI.</p></div>
    </div>
